    "The main differentiator is the presence of feedback within the network, which can originate from the hidden layer, output layer, or a combination of both.",
    "RNNs can be trained by unfolding them over time and using standard backpropagation or a variant known as Backpropagation Through Time (BPTT) [28].",
    "The CNN-RCNN model combines the strengths of both CNN and RCNN.",
    "It leverages the ability of CNNs to extract spatial features from images and the ability of RCNNs to capture Fig 5.",
    "Architecture of RNN."
